---
<!-- Professional space: bio + photo + CV links. Clean hub page. Work History is a separate page. -->
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Professional Space — Juan Pablo Bascur</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; }
      .page { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 5rem; }
      nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
      nav a { font-size: 13px; color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 1.5rem; }
      nav a:hover { color: #1a1a1a; }
      .nav-card { border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; padding: 8px 14px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: inline-block; transition: border-color 0.15s; }
      .nav-card:hover { border-color: #ccc; }
      .nav-card-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; color: #1a1a1a; }
      .nav-card-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 2px; }
      h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .prose { font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; }
      .section-title { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
      .cv-note { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .btn { font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid #ddd; color: #534AB7; text-decoration: none; }
      .btn:hover { background: #f5f5f5; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
  <div class="page">
    <nav>
      <a href="/" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: #1a1a1a;">jpbascur.com</a>
      <div>
        <a class="nav-card" href="/work-history">
          <div class="nav-card-title">Detailed Work History</div>
          <div class="nav-card-desc">Detailed resume</div>
        </a>
        <a class="nav-card" href="/publications">
          <div class="nav-card-title">Publications</div>
          <div class="nav-card-desc">Papers & preprints</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <h1>Professional Space</h1>

    <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <div style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;">
        <p class="prose">Data Scientist with 10 years of work experience, including 7 years in academia and 3 years in industry. I am passionate about helping people extract valuable insights from data and seek projects where I can both contribute and continue learning. I enjoy collaborating with colleagues and developing innovative solutions. I have experience in deploying machine learning models, deploying web based interactive visualizations, and extracting insights from data.</p>
        <div>
          <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 0;">Official CV</div>
          <p class="cv-note">The most up-to-date version of my CV.</p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
            <a class="btn" href="/files/cv.pdf" target="_blank">Open CV</a>
            <a class="btn" href="/files/cv.pdf" download>Download PDF</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/professional/phd_defence.jpeg" alt="PhD defence" style="width: 440px; border-radius: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; object-fit: cover;" />
    </div>


  </div>
  </body>
</html>
